 dlls/dcomp/Makefile.in                   |    2 ++
 dlls/dcomp/device.c                      | 1458 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 2 files changed, 1437 insertions(+), 23 deletions(-)

